casebody.head_matter:
DEPARTMENT OF HOMELAND SECURITY, et al., petitioners,
v.
REGENTS OF the UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA, et al.
No. 17-1003.
Supreme Court of the United States
Jan. 23, 2018.
The motion of petitioners to expedite consideration of the petition for writ of certiorari before judgment is granted in part. As respondents have agreed, they will file their briefs in opposition by February 2, 2018.
